{
  "1885930": {
    "name": "GIGASWORD",
    "steam_appid": 1885930,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885930/extras/db7874c4cb38bf4ba0eb9c0c4f3596f2.poster.avif?t=1769536990\" width=800 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885930/extras/db7874c4cb38bf4ba0eb9c0c4f3596f2.webm?t=1769536990\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这款动作解谜类银河战士恶魔城游戏中，剑的威力将决定一切。玩家要平衡巨剑 GIGASWORD 的重量，进行脑力和体力的挑战。Thoenhart 是一座饱受饥荒和疾病困扰的城市，随着紧张局势的加剧，城中的人类寄望于最终的解决办法：入侵古老的巢穴之塔 Nestrium，杀死夜鹰，夺取神之水晶 Gnosis 占为己有。据说这一水晶能给拥有它的人带来繁荣，因此人类世世代代都在追寻它。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >然而，在突袭它的安息之地时，人们扰乱了古老的力量，唤醒了一种能够摧毁现实结构的邪恶。Ezra 能否及时到达巢穴之塔的塔顶，阻止这场大灾难？或者，人类的无知会带领世界走向灭亡？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885930/extras/1c5ce215b105a85663d4d5d66150f69d.poster.avif?t=1769536990\" width=800 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885930/extras/1c5ce215b105a85663d4d5d66150f69d.webm?t=1769536990\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>平衡重量 -</strong> 这把巨剑也许非常适合战斗，但你会发现砍杀并不是它的唯一的用途。它可以解锁门、压下压力板、推开障碍物，你也可以把剑插在地上，徒步移动，让自己暂时卸下巨剑的重负。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885930/extras/02c5c1d9370439eea2b53337c638872a.poster.avif?t=1769536990\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885930/extras/02c5c1d9370439eea2b53337c638872a.webm?t=1769536990\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885930/extras/02c5c1d9370439eea2b53337c638872a.mp4?t=1769536990\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>古老的秘密 -</strong> 大灾难即将来临，探索被遗忘的 Nestrium 蜿蜒曲折的大厅。每个角落、缝隙和墙洞都隐藏着秘密，只有你才能发现其中蕴藏的财富。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885930/extras/c3bf6033655a23486931be9d9d337041.poster.avif?t=1769536990\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885930/extras/c3bf6033655a23486931be9d9d337041.webm?t=1769536990\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885930/extras/c3bf6033655a23486931be9d9d337041.mp4?t=1769536990\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>遏制恶魔造成的毁灭 -</strong> 劈砍、斩杀，躲避无情的恶魔、腐败的头目和嗜血魔鬼的致命袭击，将他们送回地狱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885930/extras/70c5236b58fab5e6067020f2096b1394.poster.avif?t=1769536990\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885930/extras/70c5236b58fab5e6067020f2096b1394.webm?t=1769536990\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885930/extras/70c5236b58fab5e6067020f2096b1394.mp4?t=1769536990\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>适应、创新、进化 -</strong> 在你被迫穿越邪恶的陷阱、致命的坠落和看似坚不可摧的敌人的同时，探索新的能力来帮助你完成旅程，例如雷电、爬行火花、抓钩等等！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885930/extras/42502ca59171791f323e73c79a071f96.poster.avif?t=1769536990\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885930/extras/42502ca59171791f323e73c79a071f96.webm?t=1769536990\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885930/extras/42502ca59171791f323e73c79a071f96.mp4?t=1769536990\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>为了解救饥荒和家庭 -</strong> 人类已经濒临死亡，他们诅咒上苍，希望Nestrium 能拯救他们。由夜鹰守护的神之水晶 Gnosis 是带来繁荣的机会。Ezra 必须守护平衡……并为所有人带来和平。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885930/extras/01958fcbf6ba382a48f2c8ad4bb52a11.poster.avif?t=1769536990\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885930/extras/01958fcbf6ba382a48f2c8ad4bb52a11.webm?t=1769536990\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1885930/extras/01958fcbf6ba382a48f2c8ad4bb52a11.mp4?t=1769536990\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
